<div type="cedula"><ab>Cedula <lb/>Auch hat <expan>Herdege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Valczn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> künig czü
